  "instructions": [
    "heat the oven to 400\u0000f and roast the pork bones for 30 minutes.",
    "in a large pot, combine the roasted pork bones, ginger, garlic, galangal, and lemongrass. add 4 cups of water and bring to a boil.",
    "reduce the heat and simmer for 1 hour, skimming the surface occasionally.",
    "add the fish sauce, lime juice, and bean sprouts to the pot and simmer for another 15 minutes.",
    "cook the rice noodles according to the package instructions and set aside.",
    "in a large bowl, combine the roasted red cabbage, chopped basil, and cooked noodles.",
    "strain the pork broth through a fine-mesh sieve into a bowl and discard the solids.",
    "pour the hot broth over the noodles and cabbage mixture and serve hot."
